{"tid":2349623,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)莎賓娜的顫慄冒險 第1-4季","createTime":"2021-01-01T16:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T15:43:06.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b52c584aaf0e8607208db1db3b2eff5de8f19c07","tid":2349623,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=c9e810ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=5fd75d32\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=32ec46af\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/z2029969a/1540910839-2865474471_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fz2029969a%2F1540910839-2865474471_n.jpg&h=1fd9877b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://roteironerd.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/KIERNAMINI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Froteironerd.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2FKIERNAMINI.jpg&h=7f7a8ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據漫畫《莎賓娜的顫慄冒險》(The Chilling Adventures of Sabrina)改編新劇由Netflix接手開發，直接預定兩季，共20集。將與CW大熱新劇《河谷鎮》共處一個宇宙，兩劇都是根據阿奇漫畫改編。莎賓娜是阿奇漫畫中最受歡迎的角色之一，但沒有出現在《河谷鎮》裡。故事聚焦年輕女巫Sabrina Spellman，她半人半巫，致力於與威脅到她自己、家庭以及人類性命的邪惡勢力作鬥爭。充滿超自然、恐怖、魔法、巫術等元素，風格類似《羅斯瑪麗的嬰兒》和《驅魔人》<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=2c395da7\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=9a00271a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112471280941ecf4afffddbf7469e6899d9a9de3","tid":2349623,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d126041a421b2da87dc68158f46fd12394abc1","tid":2349623,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"h